PROGRAM :

LXI H, 4200H  
MVI C, 00  
MOV A, M  
INX H  
ADD M  
JNC SKIP  
INR C  
SKIP: INX H  
MOV M, A  
INX H  
MOV M, C  
HLT

 
 SAMPLE DATA:  
          Input                                   Output 
Address          Data                 Address               Data 
4200              2F                   4202                 18  (Sum) 
4201              E9                   4203                 01  (Carry) 
